rows.label: qev090803_MSG0002
rows.name: They look nearly ready to strike the caravan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090803_MSG0003
rows.name:
Thankfully, we're completely ready.
Let's make this quick.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090803_MSG0004
rows.name: I knew the Prone had superhuman strength, but that...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090803_MSG0005
rows.name: If you hadn't been with me, I fear I would have...well, died.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090803_MSG0006
rows.name: You have my thanks. Now let's hurry back and inform Pulala.[ST:wait ]
